reviewText: The DVDs work. I remember some of the shows as I watched them. I think it got better when they filmed it in front a live audience. I just wish they would release the rest of the seasons.
I got this when my local TV network took Happy Days off the air and I have loved reliving the 50s and 60s with the Cunninghams and Fonzie.
I really enjoy American history, and this was good overview of Burr.
